OL,7,FThe leader of Kirklees Council says
OL,8,Fthe local authority has had to make
OL,9,F'painful decisions' in order to save
OL,10,F#34.5 million in the next financial
OL,11,Fyear.
OL,13,FThe budget was approved at a full
OL,14,Fcouncil meeting this evening (6
OL,15,FMarch). The spending proposals mean
OL,16,Fthe council will set a balanced budget
OL,17,Ffor the next financial year.
