OL,7,FThe local authority faced a #47
OL,8,Fmillion shortfall in its budget
OL,9,Fearlier in the year, noting an
OL,10,Fincrease in costs and demand for
OL,11,Fservices like social care for adults
OL,12,Fand children, as well as the ongoing
OL,13,Fcost-of-living crisis, as the reasons.
OL,15,FThe council says this new budget will
OL,16,F'help Kirklees avoid the fate of
OL,17,Fseveral other councils in England that
OL,18,Fhave
