OL,5,Cmillion
OL,7,F"We've had to take painful decisions
OL,8,Fto give the council financial
OL,9,Fstability. But, at the same time,
OL,10,Fwe've tried to stay true to our
OL,11,Fvalues. That means focusing our
OL,12,Fresources on the people who need our
OL,13,Fsupport most. It also means
OL,14,Fmodernising and transforming services
OL,15,Fto make them as efficient as we can.
OL,16,FAnd it means continuing to invest in
OL,17,Four future, to bring jobs and
OL,18,Fopportunities to families and
OL,19,Fcommunities in every part of Kirklees.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
