OL,4,Cdecisions' in order to save #34.5
OL,5,Cmillion
OL,7,FCouncillor Graham Turner, Cabinet
OL,8,FMember for Finance and Regeneration
OL,9,Fsaid: "All our services, from
OL,10,Fsafeguarding children to emptying
OL,11,Fbins, rely on stable funding. That's
OL,12,Fwhy it's been so important to deliver
OL,13,Fa balanced budget for residents. The
OL,14,Falternative to a balanced budget would
OL,15,Fbe worse for residents, local services
OL,16,Fand hard-working council staff.
OL,26,@qD@GOU
