OL,3,CKirklees council taking 'painful
OL,4,Cdecisions' in order to save #34.5
OL,5,Cmillion
OL,7,F"Since the cost-of-living crisis first
OL,8,Fhit, we've been reducing our costs
OL,9,Frelentlessly. We've frozen all but the
OL,10,Fmost essential recruitment and
OL,11,Fspending. We've reviewed our
OL,12,Finvestment programme and our use of
OL,13,Fbuildings. But the challenges for all
OL,14,Fcouncils are bigger than that. That's
OL,15,Fwhy we set out a long-term plan in the
OL,16,Fautumn that would reduce spending to
OL,17,Fmatch the pressures we face. This
OL,18,Fbudget achieves that fundamental
OL,19,Fresponsibility.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
