OL,3,CKirklees council taking 'painful
OL,4,Cdecisions' in order to save #34.5
OL,5,Cmillion
OL,7,F"Local government lives from hand to
OL,8,Fmouth, despite it delivering the
OL,9,Fservices that we all rely on from
OL,10,Flooking after vulnerable children to
OL,11,Fproviding adult social care, waste
OL,12,Fdisposal and maintaining roads.
OL,13,FRelying on funding from government for
OL,14,Fone year at a time makes it difficult
OL,15,Fto plan for the long term and deal
OL,16,Fwith growing demand for services. We
OL,17,Fneed a fair funding settlement that is
OL,18,Ffor several years so that we can plan
OL,19,Fahead and not be constantly budgeting
OL,20,Ffor a single year."
